I think the staff here is rather unprofessional and rude. There’s such a thing as tolerating the rudeness but it went beyond being rude. I was yelled at through the phone and then was met with comments on how I was yelling at them (I was not).

Payments and charges are a rather sketchy. If you take this review with other reviews in the page, it can be obvious this is not the place to go.

Dirty, unprofessional con artists.

First they told me they accepted my insurance Then claimed they sent me a text stating they don’t.  Then quoted me $550 for a general cleaning for a child?  Every place gave me quotes ranging from $130-$210.
The office is filthy and they make you say out loud all of your personal information in front of a crowded reception room.
